1
00:01:43,458 --> 00:01:46,208
[SERINUMA] A new <i>Mirage Saga</i>
chapter just got posted!

2
00:01:46,291 --> 00:01:47,250
So nice...

3
00:01:47,333 --> 00:01:48,708
Terra and Shion.

4
00:01:48,791 --> 00:01:51,000
Heaven. You two are perfect!

5
00:01:54,833 --> 00:01:57,875
[SERINUMA yelling]

6
00:01:57,958 --> 00:01:58,958
[SERINUMA]
Don't think about it!

7
00:01:59,041 --> 00:02:00,125
Don't think about it!

8
00:02:00,208 --> 00:02:02,500
You've gotta stop
obsessing over this!

9
00:02:02,583 --> 00:02:05,208
[NISHINA] We'll have a problem
if you don't take me seriously.

10
00:02:08,083 --> 00:02:09,666
It was a joke!

11
00:02:11,583 --> 00:02:12,666
I'm sorry!

12
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:14,541
You looked so precious,
I couldn't resist

13
00:02:14,625 --> 00:02:16,375
having a little
bit of fun with you!

14
00:02:16,458 --> 00:02:17,833
Oh, right!

15
00:02:17,916 --> 00:02:19,750
You really had me going there.

16
00:02:19,833 --> 00:02:21,708
[SERINUMA]
She's such a troublemaker!

17
00:02:21,791 --> 00:02:24,125
[NISHINA]
Do forgive me!

18
00:02:24,208 --> 00:02:26,291
[SERINUMA] It's not like the
kiss meant anything!

19
00:02:26,375 --> 00:02:28,583
Physical contact
is perfectly normal.

20
00:02:30,041 --> 00:02:31,875
Snap out of it!

21
00:02:31,958 --> 00:02:33,666
What's this?!

22
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,708
[GROUP]
A Valentine's contest?

23
00:02:35,791 --> 00:02:37,333
[SERINUMA]
I saw it on their website!

24
00:02:37,416 --> 00:02:40,666
Create a treat inspired
by a <i>Mirage Saga</i> Character.

25
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:42,208
I have to win. I need it!

26
00:02:42,291 --> 00:02:43,666
There's even a grand prize!

27
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:45,500
A drawing by the lead designer!

28
00:02:45,583 --> 00:02:47,625
I'd have to be insane
to let this rare opportunity

29
00:02:47,708 --> 00:02:48,791
slip out of my fingers!

30
00:02:48,875 --> 00:02:51,375
No! I can't let that happen!

31
00:02:52,625 --> 00:02:54,250
Let's see. What to make...

32
00:02:54,333 --> 00:02:55,333
[NISHINA]
Serinuma!

33
00:02:57,125 --> 00:02:57,875
Hello there.

34
00:02:57,958 --> 00:02:59,166
Oh. Hi!

35
00:03:01,041 --> 00:03:02,416
Please move.

36
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:04,583
I'd like to have an intimate
discussion with Serinuma.

37
00:03:04,666 --> 00:03:06,000
No surprise.

38
00:03:06,083 --> 00:03:08,583
A little bit of advice for ya...
She's not interested.

39
00:03:08,666 --> 00:03:10,166
Get lost. Now.

40
00:03:10,250 --> 00:03:11,458
Hello!

41
00:03:11,541 --> 00:03:13,416
You're entering the
Valentine contest, right?

42
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:15,750
Of course! What about you?

43
00:03:15,833 --> 00:03:16,625
[NISHINA]
Yes!

44
00:03:16,708 --> 00:03:18,833
It's exciting! Any ideas yet?

45
00:03:18,916 --> 00:03:22,000
[NISHINA] I have few things
in mind, but I'm still deciding.

46
00:03:22,083 --> 00:03:23,916
If you have any free time,

47
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,000
how about we try
each other's recipes?

48
00:03:26,083 --> 00:03:27,166
Uh...!

49
00:03:27,250 --> 00:03:29,416
Hey! You've spent
enough time with her!

50
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:31,416
You two are more
than welcome to join us.

51
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,875
Help yourselves.

52
00:03:32,958 --> 00:03:35,958
Perhaps we should invite
Mutsumi and Shinomiya as well.

53
00:03:36,041 --> 00:03:37,291
Let's do that.

54
00:03:37,375 --> 00:03:40,041
And besides... I wager
that it'll be a lot of fun

55
00:03:40,125 --> 00:03:42,000
to see you boys aching
to sample desserts

56
00:03:42,083 --> 00:03:43,541
you'll never get to eat.

57
00:03:43,625 --> 00:03:45,416
[NANASHIMA, IGARASHI]
She's such a jerk!

58
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:46,416
I'll be there!

59
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:48,166
I can make my own
desserts anyway!

60
00:03:48,250 --> 00:03:49,708
Be my guest!

61
00:03:49,791 --> 00:03:52,166
[SERINUMA] Are you ready to
make our chocolate character?

62
00:03:52,250 --> 00:03:53,791
[NISHINA]
Absolutely!

63
00:03:53,875 --> 00:03:55,458
Today we can try
a few things to see

64
00:03:55,541 --> 00:03:56,875
what works best for us!

65
00:03:56,958 --> 00:03:59,750
First, you choose
a picture of a character.

66
00:03:59,833 --> 00:04:01,791
[NISHINA]
Isn't this from my <i>doujinshi</i> ?

67
00:04:01,875 --> 00:04:03,666
Yeah! It's one of my favorites.

68
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:05,000
I should have asked you.

69
00:04:05,083 --> 00:04:06,666
Would it be all right if
I used it for the contest?

70
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:08,208
Yes!

71
00:04:08,291 --> 00:04:10,333
I'll draw a hundred more for
you if it would make you happy.

72
00:04:10,416 --> 00:04:11,625
[SERINUMA]
You're so kind.

73
00:04:11,708 --> 00:04:13,166
What do we do after that?

74
00:04:13,250 --> 00:04:15,291
[SERINUMA] First, copy the
picture onto parchment paper

75
00:04:15,375 --> 00:04:17,041
with a pencil.

76
00:04:17,125 --> 00:04:20,083
Flip it over and trace the
image with a chocolate pen.

77
00:04:20,166 --> 00:04:23,000
Then put it on the fridge
until it hardens.

78
00:04:23,083 --> 00:04:25,458
Fill in the empty spaces
with colored chocolate,

79
00:04:25,541 --> 00:04:28,166
take away the parchment
paper and voilà!

80
00:04:28,250 --> 00:04:29,708
All done!

81
00:04:29,791 --> 00:04:30,916
[GROUP]
Whoa!

82
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,833
[NANASHIMA]
It's so cool!

83
00:04:31,916 --> 00:04:33,000
That's incredible!

84
00:04:33,083 --> 00:04:34,458
With a picture like that,
they'll give you

85
00:04:34,541 --> 00:04:35,875
the win for sure.

86
00:04:39,625 --> 00:04:41,083
[SERINUMA]
It's not good enough!

87
00:04:41,166 --> 00:04:43,208
This piece of trash isn't
capturing Shion's angelic beauty

88
00:04:43,291 --> 00:04:44,875
at all!

89
00:04:44,958 --> 00:04:46,125
[SERINUMA]
I've failed him!

90
00:04:46,208 --> 00:04:49,250
I devour this pathetic
tribute as a sacrifice!

91
00:04:49,333 --> 00:04:50,708
[NANASHIMA]
Please stop...

92
00:04:52,416 --> 00:04:55,458
I think everyone chooses
character chocolates first.

93
00:04:55,541 --> 00:04:56,625
I need ideas.

94
00:04:56,708 --> 00:04:58,166
That's true.

95
00:04:58,250 --> 00:05:00,291
If you'd like to stand out,
you'll need to be more original.

96
00:05:02,541 --> 00:05:04,875
Let's make the piece 3-D.

97
00:05:04,958 --> 00:05:06,250
3-D?

98
00:05:06,333 --> 00:05:08,791
One second... a little...

99
00:05:08,875 --> 00:05:10,541
...like this!

100
00:05:10,625 --> 00:05:11,791
No way!

101
00:05:11,875 --> 00:05:13,541
Nothing less from Yokoshima.

102
00:05:13,625 --> 00:05:15,833
Brilliance pours from
everything you create.

103
00:05:15,916 --> 00:05:17,125
Happy to help.

104
00:05:18,416 --> 00:05:20,583
Together, you and I
can reach the stars!

105
00:05:20,666 --> 00:05:21,583
Okay!

106
00:05:21,666 --> 00:05:24,208
We're still here, ya know!

107
00:05:24,291 --> 00:05:25,250
[NANASHIMA]
I'm done!

108
00:05:25,333 --> 00:05:27,416
Mine turned out awesome!

109
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:29,208
My flower is the best!

110
00:05:29,291 --> 00:05:30,458
Yes, it is.

111
00:05:30,541 --> 00:05:32,625
Don't forget we're
here to support Serinuma!

112
00:05:35,541 --> 00:05:37,458
[IGARASHI] She's been working
with that thing for hours,

113
00:05:37,541 --> 00:05:39,291
but hasn't improved at all.

114
00:05:39,375 --> 00:05:40,541
[SERINUMA]
I don't get this.

115
00:05:40,625 --> 00:05:42,541
Why is it so tough to
make something in 3-D?

116
00:05:42,625 --> 00:05:44,875
Aren't I in 3-D?
Or is that 4-D?

117
00:05:44,958 --> 00:05:46,416
People make art look too easy.

118
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:47,958
Stop thinking and start working!

119
00:05:48,041 --> 00:05:50,375
If you can't figure this out,
you won't make the deadline!

120
00:05:50,458 --> 00:05:51,875
I'll help you.

121
00:05:51,958 --> 00:05:55,916
You need to relax and let
yourself have fun with it, okay?

122
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,958
Yeah.

123
00:05:57,041 --> 00:05:58,958
Thank you for the advice.

124
00:05:59,041 --> 00:06:00,375
[SERINUMA]
She's so close!

125
00:06:00,458 --> 00:06:01,500
[NANASHIMA]
Hey!

126
00:06:01,583 --> 00:06:02,708
Let her focus!

127
00:06:02,791 --> 00:06:04,541
Call me protective,
but I still don't think

128
00:06:04,625 --> 00:06:06,291
you and Serinuma
should be left alone!

129
00:06:06,375 --> 00:06:07,333
Neither do I!

130
00:06:07,416 --> 00:06:08,750
[NISHINA]
You're too rough.

131
00:06:08,833 --> 00:06:11,500
You said it yourself...
We're both girls, so why worry?

132
00:06:11,583 --> 00:06:12,583
I disagree.

133
00:06:12,666 --> 00:06:14,416
Personally, I think
Nana is dead on.

134
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:18,750
So why are you doing
all this for Serinuma?

135
00:06:18,833 --> 00:06:20,708
[NISHINA] I suppose you could
say I'm drawn to things

136
00:06:20,791 --> 00:06:22,666
that are cute and beautiful.

137
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,208
I can't help myself.

138
00:06:24,291 --> 00:06:26,458
You're saying you only
like her for her looks?

139
00:06:26,541 --> 00:06:29,041
I assure you there's
more to it than that.

140
00:06:29,125 --> 00:06:30,375
Actually...

141
00:06:30,458 --> 00:06:33,166
That sounds more like
your character than mine.

142
00:06:48,916 --> 00:06:51,458
Yes! It took me over
three days to complete,

143
00:06:51,541 --> 00:06:52,833
but it's done!

144
00:06:53,916 --> 00:06:55,958
[GROUP] That thing doesn't
look like Shion.

145
00:06:59,333 --> 00:07:00,625
[SERINUMA]
It's terrible, isn't it?

146
00:07:00,708 --> 00:07:03,208
I worked on it for so long,
I can't tell anymore!

147
00:07:03,291 --> 00:07:05,375
[NANASHIMA] It's okay!
I'd totally eat that thing!

148
00:07:05,458 --> 00:07:07,416
[MUTSUMI] It's got uniqueness
only a true artist

149
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:08,583
could capture!

150
00:07:08,666 --> 00:07:11,125
They're right!
Your eyes are drawn to it.

151
00:07:11,208 --> 00:07:14,500
I'd call it an
eccentric masterpiece!

152
00:07:14,583 --> 00:07:16,250
[SERINUMA]
Eccentric?

153
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:18,125
Idiot!

154
00:07:18,208 --> 00:07:20,166
I didn't mean it! Sorry!

155
00:07:22,958 --> 00:07:24,291
If you're comfortable with it,

156
00:07:24,375 --> 00:07:27,041
why don't you submit my design
using your name instead?

157
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,916
No way!

158
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,375
I wouldn't feel
right doing that.

159
00:07:30,458 --> 00:07:31,541
Thanks!

160
00:07:31,625 --> 00:07:33,958
Wait a sec.
Isn't the deadline tomorrow?

161
00:07:34,041 --> 00:07:35,541
If you wanna win that contest,

162
00:07:35,625 --> 00:07:38,125
using Nishina's chocolate
might be the safer bet.

163
00:07:39,250 --> 00:07:40,291
[GROUP]
That's true.

164
00:07:48,208 --> 00:07:50,500
[SERINUMA] I spent so
much time practicing.

165
00:07:58,375 --> 00:08:00,000
[SERINUMA]
It's so sweet.

166
00:08:00,083 --> 00:08:01,958
Everything is clear now.

167
00:08:02,041 --> 00:08:03,625
I know what I have to do.

168
00:08:03,708 --> 00:08:06,416
What? You ended up sending
in the one you made?

169
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:07,458
You did?

170
00:08:07,541 --> 00:08:08,875
Was there something
wrong with mine?

171
00:08:08,958 --> 00:08:10,375
Not at all.

172
00:08:10,458 --> 00:08:12,416
I thought about how it was
supposed to be a Valentine.

173
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,041
It's special when you
get something like that

174
00:08:14,125 --> 00:08:15,500
from another person.

175
00:08:15,583 --> 00:08:16,958
It was hard to look at,

176
00:08:17,041 --> 00:08:18,541
but it came straight
from my heart.

177
00:08:18,625 --> 00:08:20,708
There's no way I could
use anyone else's.

178
00:08:20,791 --> 00:08:22,666
I'm really sorry
for wasting your time!

179
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,000
Don't worry!

180
00:08:24,083 --> 00:08:25,750
You're such a loving person.

181
00:08:25,833 --> 00:08:28,000
That's what makes you wonderful.

182
00:08:28,083 --> 00:08:30,125
Well, what a nice
thing for you to say!

183
00:08:30,208 --> 00:08:31,375
I almost forgot.

184
00:08:31,458 --> 00:08:32,791
Here you go!

185
00:08:32,875 --> 00:08:35,208
It's a small gift to say thanks
for being so nice to me.

186
00:08:35,291 --> 00:08:36,500
I hope you like it.

187
00:08:43,791 --> 00:08:45,500
This chocolate is really good.

188
00:08:45,583 --> 00:08:46,583
Yeah.

189
00:08:46,666 --> 00:08:48,125
She's pretty cute, huh?

190
00:08:51,958 --> 00:08:54,500
You're saying you only
like her for her looks?

191
00:08:54,583 --> 00:08:57,666
That sounds more like
your character than mine.

192
00:08:57,750 --> 00:09:00,416
[IGARASHI] In the beginning,
it was about her looks.

193
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:01,791
But now...

194
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:09,166
[IGARASHI]
I don't wanna give her up.

195
00:09:09,250 --> 00:09:13,041
I had no way of knowing that
a time was coming very soon

196
00:09:13,125 --> 00:09:15,250
where my feelings
would be put to the test.

197
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:19,125
[IGARASHI]
Serinuma?

198
00:09:23,083 --> 00:09:24,791
Oh. Hi!

199
00:09:36,250 --> 00:09:37,250
[NAKANO]
Huh?

200
00:09:39,958 --> 00:09:40,958
[NAKANO]
Kae?

201
00:09:42,166 --> 00:09:43,250
Yeah? What's up?

202
00:09:43,333 --> 00:09:44,958
Uh, what... what happened?

203
00:09:45,041 --> 00:09:46,916
It's just been a... weekend!

204
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,500
[SERINUMA laughs]
Funny story!

205
00:09:48,583 --> 00:09:50,875
I had a ton of that Valentine
chocolate left over,

206
00:09:50,958 --> 00:09:53,375
and you can't let that stuff
go to waste, right?

207
00:09:53,458 --> 00:09:55,291
Over the weekend
I started nibbling...

208
00:09:55,375 --> 00:09:56,791
...and nibbling...
and before I knew it,

209
00:09:56,875 --> 00:09:58,291
they were all gone!

210
00:09:58,375 --> 00:10:00,166
Next thing I knew
I looked like this!

211
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:01,291
Crazy, huh?

212
00:10:05,333 --> 00:10:06,791
Good morning!

213
00:10:06,875 --> 00:10:09,125
Oh, really? Is it?

214
00:10:09,208 --> 00:10:11,416
Are you feeling okay?

215
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:13,583
We learned in health class that
it's unsafe for your weight

216
00:10:13,666 --> 00:10:15,125
to fluctuate quickly.

217
00:10:15,208 --> 00:10:18,458
I appreciate you checking
on me, but I feel great!

218
00:10:18,541 --> 00:10:19,500
[laughs]

219
00:10:22,958 --> 00:10:24,291
Nana!

220
00:10:24,375 --> 00:10:25,791
[SERINUMA] I'll go get the
teacher! Just hold on!

221
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:27,083
[SHINOMIYA]
What's wrong?!

222
00:10:27,166 --> 00:10:28,250
[yelps]

223
00:10:30,125 --> 00:10:31,083
[SERINUMA]
Shinomiya!

224
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:34,416
Oh, no! Please wake up!

225
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:36,916
We need help!

226
00:10:39,083 --> 00:10:41,375
[SHINOMIYA] A dream. A dream.
This is a dream!

227
00:10:41,458 --> 00:10:43,666
I'll close my eyes and drift
into a peaceful slumber,

228
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:45,750
and when I wake up Serinuma
will be normal again!

229
00:10:45,833 --> 00:10:48,208
Right. She's gonna have
to lose the weight!

230
00:10:48,291 --> 00:10:50,916
[IGARASHI] I don't think there's
anything we can do about it.

231
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,666
Well not with that attitude.

232
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:55,500
And don't say anything about
her having a good personality.

233
00:10:55,583 --> 00:10:58,750
You're as bad as we are,
Mr. High and Mighty!

234
00:10:58,833 --> 00:11:01,458
What's the point if she
doesn't have a hot body?

235
00:11:01,541 --> 00:11:04,000
You're awful. That's offensive.

236
00:11:04,083 --> 00:11:05,333
But...

237
00:11:05,416 --> 00:11:06,541
I'm with you!

238
00:11:06,625 --> 00:11:07,791
Yeah, boy!

239
00:11:07,875 --> 00:11:08,833
Wow.

240
00:11:12,416 --> 00:11:13,375
Oh, wow!

241
00:11:13,458 --> 00:11:14,666
This is delicious!

242
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:16,125
Are you sure you
don't want some?

243
00:11:16,208 --> 00:11:17,958
No way, it's all yours!

244
00:11:20,208 --> 00:11:22,000
[NANASHIMA growls]

245
00:11:22,083 --> 00:11:24,000
Why are you feeding
her all this food?!

246
00:11:24,083 --> 00:11:26,125
Hey, Nanashima, you should
try a bite of this thing.

247
00:11:26,208 --> 00:11:28,666
Are you any feeling
better now, Shinomiya?

248
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:30,500
Did you give her
all of these desserts?

249
00:11:30,583 --> 00:11:31,666
I'm afraid so.

250
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:33,375
Her body is so
beautiful and soft

251
00:11:33,458 --> 00:11:34,666
that I want to
keep feeding her.

252
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:36,333
I can't stop myself!

253
00:11:36,416 --> 00:11:39,083
[NISHINA laughing]

254
00:11:39,166 --> 00:11:41,208
You're tickling me, Shima.
Cut it out!

255
00:11:41,291 --> 00:11:43,375
[SHINOMIYA, NANASHIMA]
You're not helping!

256
