515
00:21:36,291 --> 00:21:39,375
[GROUP] We gave up so much...
for the cause.

516
00:21:39,458 --> 00:21:42,625
[NANASHIMA] I don't know if
the sacrifice was worth it.

517
00:21:42,708 --> 00:21:45,083
[SHINOMIYA] We should've
given it more thought.

518
00:21:45,166 --> 00:21:48,375
There's only one reward left.
I can't wait for this!

519
00:21:48,458 --> 00:21:49,583
[BOTH gasp]

520
00:21:49,666 --> 00:21:50,958
[IGARASHI]
What's that?!

521
00:21:51,041 --> 00:21:52,708
[NISHINA] I added it to give
her further incentive.

522
00:21:52,791 --> 00:21:54,000
Just a little smooch.

523
00:21:54,083 --> 00:21:55,416
[NANASHIMA]
Hell no!

524
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:58,000
Show the one you adore
you respect her hard work.

525
00:21:58,083 --> 00:21:59,166
You wanted this.

526
00:21:59,250 --> 00:22:00,541
[NANASHIMA yelling]

527
00:22:02,083 --> 00:22:03,250
[NANASHIMA]
Wait!

528
00:22:03,333 --> 00:22:05,125
What are you doing? Stop it!

529
00:22:08,916 --> 00:22:09,875
[BOTH yelp]

530
00:22:09,958 --> 00:22:12,750
[BOTH whimpering]

531
00:22:13,708 --> 00:22:16,583
[NAKANO] And so... the <i>Mirage</i>
<i>Saga</i> Valentine Contest

532
00:22:16,666 --> 00:22:19,875
Award Ceremony went even
better than she expected!

533
00:23:50,666 --> 00:23:52,000
[MUTSUMI]
What's the matter, Shinomiya?

534
00:23:52,083 --> 00:23:53,250
You seem down.

535
00:23:53,333 --> 00:23:54,333
[SHINOMIYA] There was a
fight in my class today

536
00:23:54,416 --> 00:23:55,833
and I got stuck in
the middle of it.

537
00:23:55,916 --> 00:23:57,041
We all got in scolded.

538
00:23:57,125 --> 00:23:58,625
[MUTSUMI]
That doesn't sound like you.

539
00:23:58,708 --> 00:23:59,833
What happened?

540
00:23:59,916 --> 00:24:01,291
[SHINOMIYA]
They stuffed my head in a toilet

541
00:24:01,375 --> 00:24:02,750
when I reminded them that
fighting is for degenerates

542
00:24:02,833 --> 00:24:04,000
with too much free time.

543
00:24:04,083 --> 00:24:05,000
[MUTSUMI]
Poor thing.

544
00:24:05,083 --> 00:24:06,583
I hope you didn't get hurt.

545
00:24:06,666 --> 00:24:07,916
Let me comfort your ego.

546
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:09,333
[SHINOMIYA]
Uh... no thanks.

547
00:24:09,416 --> 00:24:11,875
Physical rough-housing
isn't exactly my strong suit.

548
00:24:11,958 --> 00:24:14,125
I'll use my mind to
outwit those idiots.

549
00:24:14,208 --> 00:24:15,166
[MUTSUMI]
Oh, I see.

550
00:24:15,250 --> 00:24:16,375
Well, good luck!

551
00:24:16,458 --> 00:24:18,208
[SHINOMIYA]
Mutsumi, are you a good fighter?

